1
00:01:12,080 --> 00:01:12,880
Brother.

2
00:01:13,600 --> 00:01:16,260
You've done so much for Dayang Village already.

3
00:01:16,600 --> 00:01:18,600
You've cheated death so many times.

4
00:01:19,080 --> 00:01:19,880
Brother.

5
00:01:20,320 --> 00:01:22,160
If you go provoke Xiao Tianman again,

6
00:01:22,160 --> 00:01:23,890
how many lives do you have left?

7
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:24,600
Fine.

8
00:01:24,600 --> 00:01:27,120
Even if we manage to steal the voice recorder,

9
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:29,580
can you guarantee Gao Shan will protect you?

10
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:32,440
Gao Shan just wants to use it to blackmail Xiao Tianman.

11
00:01:32,440 --> 00:01:33,880
They're all businessmen.

12
00:01:33,880 --> 00:01:34,680
Exactly.

13
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:37,479
How long has he had that ledger?

14
00:01:37,479 --> 00:01:39,539
Look at... All right, that's enough.

15
00:01:44,039 --> 00:01:47,560
If what Gao Shan says is true,

16
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:50,000
this time,

17
00:01:51,520 --> 00:01:53,920
we can definitely bring down Xiao Tianman.

18
00:01:54,160 --> 00:01:55,360
So no matter what,

19
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,680
I have to take the risk.

20
00:01:59,039 --> 00:02:00,900
It's a long shot, but I have to try.

21
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:07,720
So are you two coming with me,

22
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:08,600
or not?

23
00:02:12,880 --> 00:02:13,680
I'm in.

24
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:16,000
I'm in.

25
00:02:21,920 --> 00:02:23,320
Thank you, Brother Xiao.

26
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:25,960
This gathering is long overdue.

27
00:02:27,480 --> 00:02:30,200
I should have invited you to get together ages ago.

28
00:02:30,200 --> 00:02:32,120
Don't "Brother Xiao" me.

29
00:02:32,440 --> 00:02:33,880
Don't butter me up.

30
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:35,360
Brother Xiao.

31
00:02:35,880 --> 00:02:37,480
Please don't make this awkward for me.

32
00:02:37,480 --> 00:02:39,480
The reason I asked you here,

33
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:42,520
is to apologize to you.

34
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:48,079
Apologize?

35
00:02:54,040 --> 00:02:54,960
I don't get it.

36
00:02:54,960 --> 00:02:55,720
Mr. Gao.

37
00:02:56,640 --> 00:02:58,300
What are you apologizing for?

38
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:00,780
Brother Xiao, it's like this.

39
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:04,170
It really was a misunderstanding.

40
00:03:04,920 --> 00:03:08,640
My men did take Yang Gang's gold.

41
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:14,840
But I really knew nothing about it.

42
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:17,970
By the time I found out, it was too late.

43
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:21,560
That was when I realized this gold mine belongs to you.

44
00:03:24,320 --> 00:03:29,640
So, how do you want to handle this, Boss Gao?

45
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,800
It was indeed my fault.

46
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:33,820
How about this?

47
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:39,560
I'll pay you back three times the value of the gold.

48
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:46,560
And I'll formally apologize to you.

49
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:47,690
Is that acceptable?

50
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:51,200
Gao Shan, do you think

51
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:53,880
I need this money?

52
00:03:55,640 --> 00:03:57,770
I really want to take this opportunity

53
00:03:59,200 --> 00:04:01,920
for us to bury the hatchet.

54
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:17,279
Let's climb in from the back.

55
00:04:18,279 --> 00:04:20,519
What's there to fear with you here, Boss?

56
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:21,040
Let's go.

57
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:22,000
How do we climb?

58
00:04:22,840 --> 00:04:24,700
You don't know how to climb a wall?

59
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:29,880
Come on, brothers. Here's to Second Brother.

60
00:04:30,320 --> 00:04:32,400
May he lead us to make a fortune.

61
00:04:33,159 --> 00:04:34,480
To Second Brother.

62
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:48,130
Keep it down.

63
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:54,080
Split up and search.

64
00:04:54,080 --> 00:04:54,840
All right.

65
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:23,720
Sun.

66
00:05:26,880 --> 00:05:28,600
Go upstairs and get two bottles of wine.

67
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:29,400
Which ones?

68
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:31,760
The two bottles from '82.

69
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:36,680
The ones Mr. Xiao has been saving?

70
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:39,120
Right.

71
00:05:43,080 --> 00:05:43,940
Think about it.

72
00:05:45,440 --> 00:05:47,370
We risk our lives for him every day.

73
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:50,290
If we're drinking his wine,

74
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:52,980
why not drink the expensive ones?

75
00:05:53,159 --> 00:05:53,760
Exactly.

76
00:05:56,840 --> 00:05:57,900
Let's have a drink.

77
00:06:13,960 --> 00:06:14,760
It's locked.

78
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:16,120
Give me the knife.

79
00:06:36,440 --> 00:06:38,159
They're all from '82.

80
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:40,480
Drink up.

81
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:51,610
Second Brother.

82
00:06:52,320 --> 00:06:53,159
Found it.

83
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:54,560
Let me tell you,

84
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:56,320
this is great wine.

85
00:06:57,080 --> 00:06:59,080
Drink more. Don't try to weasel out.

86
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:00,400
Drink it all down.

87
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:02,200
Fill that glass up for me.

88
00:07:02,840 --> 00:07:03,170
Okay.

89
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,720
Finish it all.

90
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:06,240
You got it.

91
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:14,800
Boss Gao.

92
00:07:16,760 --> 00:07:19,020
You can't do business in Dayang Village.

93
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:22,640
That's an unwritten rule between us, isn't it?

94
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:24,320
But there's one thing.

95
00:07:24,320 --> 00:07:25,640
You made a good point.

96
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:28,640
We do need an opportunity

97
00:07:29,080 --> 00:07:30,480
to bury the hatchet.

98
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:33,500
I'll drink to that.

99
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:37,380
Thanks, Brother Xiao.

100
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:45,600
See?

101
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:50,520
Look.

102
00:07:52,640 --> 00:07:54,840
We built this empire with our own hands.

103
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:57,880
Why should we hand it to Shanshui Group?

104
00:07:58,840 --> 00:08:00,370
Now they're targeting you.

105
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:02,520
Later on,

106
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:07,640
it'll be my turn.

107
00:08:08,960 --> 00:08:09,680
What if I told you

108
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:11,800
that I've never taken Situ Hongtang seriously?

109
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:13,000
Would you believe me?

110
00:08:15,760 --> 00:08:17,690
As long as I, Xiao Tianman, am here,

111
00:08:17,960 --> 00:08:20,220
she won't be able to restructure easily.

112
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:22,280
You know the saying,

113
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:26,410
'A mighty dragon is no match for the local snake.'

114
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:27,400
Right?

115
00:08:28,080 --> 00:08:30,840
Besides, Situ Hongtang is no dragon.

116
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:43,480
Let me check again. Okay.

117
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:02,000
The photos.

118
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:08,400
Found them. Let's go.

119
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:17,960
Don't leave without me.

120
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:19,720
Give me a hand.

121
00:09:22,320 --> 00:09:23,120
Gao.

122
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:26,000
You really picked the right moment.

123
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:30,400
From now on, we're brothers.

124
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:40,920
Brother Xiao.

125
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:46,160
I heard there's a recording pen.

126
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:48,680
It's small and convenient.

127
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:51,620
But it's hard for me to get one.

128
00:09:52,760 --> 00:09:54,040
Can you get it?

129
00:09:55,680 --> 00:09:56,810
What recording pen?

130
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:06,040
By the way,

131
00:10:08,560 --> 00:10:11,420
doesn't Jiang Xiaomei have the same recording pen?

132
00:10:17,720 --> 00:10:18,920
Who is Jiang Xiaomei?

133
00:10:21,680 --> 00:10:22,880
What recording pen?

134
00:10:27,560 --> 00:10:28,890
Nothing, Brother Xiao.

135
00:10:31,160 --> 00:10:32,240
I just wanted to borrow

136
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:34,160
Jiang Xiaomei's recording pen.

137
00:10:34,400 --> 00:10:36,120
Don't tell me you didn't know

138
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:37,440
that she left a recording pen in your drawer?

139
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:38,800
Just you wait.
